Source: pgmonitor
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/CrunchyData/pgmonitor-extension

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgmonitor
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pgmonitor
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Collector-friendly PostgreSQL metrics for PGVERSION
 pgmonitor provides metric views, materialized views, tables, and an optional
 background worker that refreshes stored metrics for external collectors.
